 href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fvrsubmit.htm&d=vndMBExpkEaUQx9ttGHWPnXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=376efed2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>用email/fax交 今晚1200截</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">如你持有有效的香港郵政或電子核證服務有限公司的電子核證（個人）證書 &lt;- 呢個基本冇人有，所以唔使試</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">免費傳真方法 </span></strong><br />\nHelloFax 免費黑白5張 / FAX.PLUS 免費黑白10張<br />\n<br />\n【教學】選民登記7月2日截止仲未搞？ 教你手機內3分鐘完成手續<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F06%2F17%2Fvotersubmit%2Fsoftware%2Fandroid-app%2F&d=vndMBExpkEaUQx9ttGHWPnXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=bab65ff5\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/</a><br />\n<br />\n[置頂]2019選民登記 推爆佢 7月2號截止<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1263306\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1263306</a><br />\n[/麻煩大家幫手share出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />]"},{"pid":"39ba4747a462c58144c1c23e20ac7bd91aacefe9","tid":1278430,"uid":269052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:38:43.000Z","msg":"重要既要講十萬次 千祈唔好道歉<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1278092\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1278092</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1283b854f9b348ef80a9a7d5c17b480f5c30a5fd","tid":1278430,"uid":133903,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"44db9234dba9c4200b41fdb660d374ceafc333ba","tid":1278430,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":326,"score":-326,"quote":{"pid":"4e24ecf1adcb8d3e7